    "first_run_id": "2026-06-30-be-tax-benefit",
    "notes": [
      "The adapter promotes ELI metadata, Moniteur/Staatsblad legal-authority URLs, Justel consolidation locators, and provision slices into corpus citation paths.",
      "The 2026-06-30 Belgium tax-benefit run now writes 3,304 provisions with complete coverage across federal, Brussels, Flemish, and Walloon statute/regulation classes, including 1981 social-security principles, 1980 union-premium law locators, the 1994 coordinated health-insurance law, its 3 July 1996 implementing decree, Royal Decree No. 38 self-employed social-status article slices, Royal Decree No. 33 invalidity/prepension withholding instruments, Royal Decree No. 50 worker pension provisions, and the 23 December 1996 worker-pension implementing decree.",
      "Separate official-document ingestion snapshots current CIR 1992 consolidated text into corpus run 2026-06-30-be-income-tax-consolidated after upstream ELI/Moniteur CIR 1992 locators are identified; the current consolidation is used for article-level income-year 2025 / assessment-year 2026 text because Justel warns that HTML consolidated updates are suspended."
    ]
  },
  "source_acquisition": {
    "source_priority": [
      {
        "rank": 1,
        "source": "Moniteur belge / Belgisch Staatsblad ELI Moniteur link",
        "use": "Original publication and official publication image/PDF."
      },
      {
        "rank": 2,
        "source": "Justel ELI consolidated version",
        "use": "Current consolidated text locator and amendment navigation only; not authentic legal text."
      },
      {
        "rank": 3,
        "source": "Agency guidance or calculators",
        "use": "Operational rates and examples after upstream law is identified."
      }
    ],
    "eli_url_template": "https://www.ejustice.just.fgov.be/eli/<document_type>/<yyyy>/<mm>/<dd>/<numac>/<moniteur|justel>",
